Package nl.strohalm.cyclos.dao

Interface Summary
ApplicationDAO DAO interface for application
BaseDAO<E extends Entity> Base Data Access Object which all DAO interface should extend.
DeletableDAO<E extends Entity> DAO interface for DAO's that can perform delete on their entities
FetchDAO This componente provides mechanisms for lazy loading and fetching lazy relationships for persistent entities in the system.
IndexedDAO<E extends Entity & Indexable> DAO interface for DAO's that are indexed for full text searches
IndexOperationDAO DAO interface for IndexOperation
InsertableDAO<E extends Entity> DAO interface for DAO's that can perform inserts on their entities
JDBCCallback Interface for JDBC works
UpdatableDAO<E extends Entity> DAO interface for DAO's that can perform updates on their entities

BaseDAOImpl<E extends Entity> Basic implementation for DAOs, extending Spring Framework support for Hibernate 3.
FetchDAOImpl Implementation for fetch DAO
IndexedDAOImpl<E extends Entity & Indexable> Base implementation for indexed DAOs
IndexOperationDAOImpl Implementation for IndexOperationDAO
